                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>eo</ex></expan> Silvano <lb n="2"/>Lucios <note>sic</note> Cinonis <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Stehender Silvanus in Tunica und Mantel, flankert von Hunden. Die Inschrift befindet sich auf dem Sockel. In mehrere aneinanderpassende Fragmente zerbrochen.</p>
            </div>
